- phone_number (string) (optional) | MY ISO PhoneNumber Eg: +6018-2031218 or 0060182031218 or 006018-2031218

- working_opening_hours (time) (optional) | format: 'H:m:s'
- working_closing_hours (time) (optional) | format: 'H:m:s'
- time_order_open (time) (optional) | format: 'H:m:s'
- time_order_close (time) (optional) | format: 'H:m:s'
- delivery_fee (decimal) (optional)
- disable_ordering (bit) (optional) | 1 or 0
-

- name (string)
- status halal (bit) | 1 or 0
- image (string) | Image URL
- longitude (double)
- latitude (double)
- rank (decimal)
- featured (bit) | 1 or 0
- halal (bit) | 1 or 0
